5065 - Electronic Parts and Equipment, Not Elsewhere Classified Summary > SENNHEISER AUSTRALIA PTY LIMITED is an Australian proprietary company. Its operations cover electronic parts and equipment, not elsewhere classified. The company is involved in the import but not export of goods. SENNHEISER AUSTRALIA PTY LIMITED is headquartered in Chatswood, New South Wales. It is headed by chief executive officer Daniel Sennheiser. For the 2024 financial year, the company reported revenue of $30.27 million. Its net profit totalled $357,000. SENNHEISER AUSTRALIA PTY LIMITED forms part of the wholesale trade industry sector.
